### Buscar Kit por ID
# Substitua {id} pelo UUID do kit
GET {{baseUrl}}/exames/kits/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 200 OK
# {
#   "id": "uuid",
#   "codigoInterno": "KIT-CHECKUP-001",
#   "nomeKit": "Kit Check-up Básico",
#   "tipoKit": "CHECK_UP",
#   "statusKit": "ATIVO",
#   "valorTotal": 350.00,
#   "precoKit": 280.00,
#   "kitExames": [ ... ],
#   ...
# }


### Buscar Kit por Código Interno
GET {{baseUrl}}/exames/kits/codigo/KIT-CHECKUP-001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 200 OK
# { ... dados do kit ... }


